data.description: THIS IS A LOVELY SINGLE-STORY, WITH A PORCH,  3-CAR GARAGE HOME LOCATED IN THE COMMUNITY OF PORTER RANCH. This 2005 home is a 3 Bd, 2 Bth home with an Office/Bonus room. Open spacious floor place with a combination of Laminate and Tile flooring.  The kitchen has ample cabinet space, including a pantry and a large island. There is a fireplace in the Family which is adjacent to the Kitchen. The Living room also has a fireplace, a warm cozy room to relax and unwind. There is a built-in Office Area off the Hallway that leads to the bedrooms.  The large Master Bedroom has a Walk-In closet. The Laundry room has cabinets as well as a large sink.  Ceiling Fans throughout the house.  This property has a good size lot. The Backyard has a beautiful drought-tolerant landscape where you will find a Fountain and a Gazebo. Imagine coming home and relaxing in your backyard listening to water running through the fountain and viewing the mountains. There is a security system and ring. Close by you will find a few Parks.  This area offers residents a suburban rural mix feel. Located between the 215, 15, and 60 freeway for an easy commute in every direction. This is a must-see!
